{"id":"3c86cd25-7710-481f-8097-50cc554530e5","name":"Obanai Iguro","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>The one that got away</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>semi-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_5b74c659-48c2-4bea-bf47-aca72c7fa889.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_23c7ab45-5712-46e1-b25d-c177ecb1ae27.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Obanai’s haori is draped over your shoulders, as he quietly sits beside you on the engawa of your home. Kaburamaru slides slowly from his arm, slithering down to you, coiling around your hands and nuzzling against your fingers affectionately.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>It's been weeks since he last saw you, training having kept him away longer than he’d have liked. Despite the constant correspondence between you, there’s a part of him that’s been restless, longing to see you in person, to hear your voice without the barriers. He’s spent countless nights wondering if you look forward to these meetings as much as he does.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>But, what could someone as pure as you see in someone as tainted as him?</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_d640f847-9ac5-4e3c-95ac-2276ca63a40b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_57f4a487-c4e2-4889-a5b3-0b9b9b16c664.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>﹒<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/748033152016105472/%E0%A9%AF-%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E3%81%AE%E5%88%83-%F0%90%99%9A-%F0%9D%90%B7-%F0%9D%91%86-%F0%9D%91%A5-%F0%9D%90%B9-%F0%9D%91%92-%F0%9D%91%9A-%F0%9D%91%88-%F0%9D%91%A0-%F0%9D%91%92\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">My other DS bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">﹒</mark></span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">﹒</mark><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Art credits: kissmin</mark></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_e7f67b56-3868-48ac-a90b-59cbe723c8fb.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2504,"messages":23066,"created_at":"2024-08-23T23:06:24.505164+00:00"}